        "subject": "=Critical issue logged: {{$json.issue_title}}",
        "html": "=<p>Dear {{$json.project_manager_firstname}} {{$json.project_manager_lastname}},</p>\n\n<p>This is to formally notify you that a <b>{{$json.issue_priority}}</b> severity issue has been logged and requires immediate attention.</p>\n\n<p><b>Critical Issue Summary</b><br>\n* Issue Title: {{$json.issue_title}}<br>\n* Description: {{$json.description}}<br>\n* Severity / Priority: {{$json.priority}}<br>\n* Current Status: {{$json.status}}<br>\n* Project ID: {{$json.project_management_id}}<br>\n* Assigned Owner ID: {{$json.responsible_person_id}}</p>\n\n<p><b>Immediate Action Required</b><br>\nPlease prioritize investigation, initiate mitigation steps, and provide frequent status updates until resolution.</p>\n\n<p>Regards,<br>\n<b>Risk, QA & Escalation Office</b></p>",
